latestIgtvVideos.title: Moving Frames
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Being a teacher has been a very big part of my life, be it at the regular class or workshops of Natyasocial or as a dance teacher at a school. I've been teaching at a school for 5 years now, teaching kids of various age group. Every Morning 8.30am to 1pm

I get to explore another side of my dancing journey where I get to do exactly the opposite of what you've been watching. The experience of teaching in a school has helped me learn many new things and gain valuable experience. 

A special mention to my mentor, co-teacher @shrutidatar I've created this piece with her and i've learnt alot of things from her

I hope y'all like this video created for art festival at the school

Shot & Edited by @anmoltawde

latestIgtvVideos.title: Instagram chat with Vinayak!
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Hi guys.. Here is a part of the live interactive series of mine. I am posting this one in particular because it was a fun live where I got a chance to interact with so many people across the globe. We spoke about not only dance but also life, the current situation and many such things. It was not only a fun interactive session but at the same time a very motivatonal one. I hope you like this because I got motivated and hope you do too.
